definitions.definition: A flirtatious , impudent , or pert young woman .
( derogatory , dated ) A promiscuous woman; also, a mistress ( “ the other woman in an extramarital relationship ” ) or a prostitute .

main_definition: A flirtatious , impudent , or pert young woman .
